<!-- 기본 승인 항목 상세 템플릿 (타입별 커스텀 템플릿이 없을 때 사용) -->
<div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
  <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
    <%= presenter.type_label %> 정보
  </h2>
  
  <dl class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <div>
      <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">신청자</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900">
        <%= presenter.owner_name %>
        <% if presenter.organization %>
          <span class="text-gray-500">(<%= presenter.organization.name %>)</span>
        <% end %>
      </dd>
    </div>
    
    <div>
      <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">신청일</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900">
        <%= item.created_at.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M') %>
      </dd>
    </div>
    
    <% if presenter.status %>
      <div>
        <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">상태</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900">
          <%= presenter.status %>
        </dd>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    
    <% if presenter.amount %>
      <div>
        <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">금액</dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <%= presenter.formatted_amount %>
        </dd>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </dl>
  
  <% if presenter.description %>
    <div class="mt-4">
      <dt class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500">설명</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-900">
        <%= presenter.description %>
      </dd>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  
  <% if presenter.metadata.any? %>
    <div class="mt-4 border-t pt-4">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-3">추가 정보</h3>
      <dl class="space-y-2">
        <% presenter.metadata.each do |key, value| %>
          <div class="flex">
            <dt class="text-sm text-gray-500 w-1/3"><%= key.to_s.humanize %>:</dt>
            <dd class="text-sm text-gray-900 w-2/3"><%= value %></dd>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </dl>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>